  • Constructor Details

    • Movie

      public Movie(String movieTitle, int movieRuntime, Movie.dimension dims, Movie.status movieStatus, boolean blockbuster, String movieSypnosis, String director, String[] cast, String movieRating)
      Constructor to create a Movie object with its attributes initialized
      Parameters:
      movieTitle - Title of movie to be created
      movieRuntime - Runtime of movie to be created
      dims - Dimension of movie to be created
      movieStatus - Status of movie to be created
      blockbuster - Check whether the movie to be created is a blockbuster
      movieSypnosis - Sypnosis of movie to be created
      director - Name of director of the movie to be created
      cast - Names of the male and female lead of the movie to be created
      movieRating - Rating of the movie to be created (PG, PG13, M18, R21)

    • Movie

      public Movie()
      Alternative constructor to create a Movie with 0 parameters Initialize rating of movie to be created to be a 1D array of size 6 . Initialize past reviews of movie to be created to be an empty ArrayList of type string. Intialize average rating of movie to be created to be 0.
